DQ Compiler Licensing
=====================

This repository contains components under different open-source licenses.

Compiler implementation
-----------------------

The DQ compiler implementation, including the C++ source code, is licensed
under the MIT License.

SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

See:

    LICENSES/MIT.txt

Runtime library and standard packages
-------------------------------------

The DQ runtime library and DQ standard packages are licensed under the
Apache License 2.0 with LLVM Exception.

SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception

See:

    LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt
    LICENSES/LLVM-exception.txt

Generated programs
------------------

Programs compiled with DQ may be distributed under terms chosen by the
program author. The DQ project does not impose a license on user programs
merely because they were compiled with DQ.

Individual source files declare their applicable license using SPDX license
identifiers in the file header.